    <item>
      <title>保守党民调不佳，苏纳克押注 7 月 4 日大选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-22/uk-general-election-will-be-held-on-july-4-bbc-reports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 宣布英国将于 7 月 4 日举行大选，这是一场比预期提前投票的重大赌博，因为他领导的保守党在民意调查中远远落后于基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 领导的反对党工党。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-22/uk-general-election-will-be-held-on-july-4-bbc-reports</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 15:32:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国将推动欧盟范围内更严格的行业气候规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-22/germany-to-push-for-stricter-eu-wide-climate-rules-for-industry</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国将游说欧盟制定更严格的气候法规，以迅速减少化石燃料重工业的排放，在欧盟选民准备前往投票站之际，这一举动可能会引起争议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-22/germany-to-push-for-stricter-eu-wide-climate-rules-for-industry</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 11:25:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
